data.description: Fantastic ranch with 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths situated on 5.84 acres offers a perfect blend of county living and modern amenities.  This home features a rocking chair front porch perfect for enjoying your morning coffee.  Laminated hardwood floors throughout, a nice-sized master suite, and a large laundry room.   The in-law suite has its own kitchen, bathroom and entrance it is perfect for guests and extended family. The home is on a full unfinished basement with endless possibilities. With plenty of land to explore, this property is an ideal place to enjoy all your outdoor activities.  Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this house your new home.
